# Autonomi Sandy Pixel-DeFi Style

## Palette
- **Background**: deep brown `#1a1310`
- **Primary**: sandy orange `#f59e0b`, rich ochre `#d97706`
- **Secondary**: muted sand `#78350f`
- **Borders**: earthy tones; cards use thin borders + subtle glow on active

## Typography
- Headers: blocky, tech-focused (e.g. Space Grotesque or pixel font)
- Body: highly legible

## Components
- **Cards**: Dark semi-transparent bg, `backdrop-filter: blur()`, thin earthy border; active/primary get accent box-shadow
- **Buttons**: Bold, sharp corners or 4px radius. Primary: `#f59e0b` bg, dark text
- **Gauges**: Blocky progress bars; LTV gradient green → yellow → orange/red, stepped/pixelated
- **Icons**: 16-bit pixel style (water drop USDC, spice USYC, stork oracle)
- **Spacing**: 16px / 8px grid; pixel-perfect alignment

## Terminology (use exactly)
Collateral Deposit (USYC), USDC Loan, Portfolio Rebalance, Yield Harvested, LTV Power Gauge, Stork Oracle, Circle Managed Wallets. Footer: "Built on Arc • Powered by Circle • Guarded by Stork". Price badge: "USYC Price: $1.05 [Stork ✓]"

## Layout
Mobile-first; single-column; clear bottom nav. Sample stats: TVL $12.4M, AVG APY 12.8%, Settlement &lt;1s.
